In Monday 's court filing , Mueller — who was appointed to investigate any collusion between Russia and the Trump campaign — said that Manafort attempted to tamper with potential witnesses . Mueller also implored the judge overseeing the case to revise or even revoke an order that had released Manafort — who was released in October after an arraignment — ahead of his trial .
